description: Data Transfer Object (DTO) class for returning Note data via API in a notes management backend.

classes.name: NoteResponse
classes.description: DTO class representing note data for API responses.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the UUID identifier of the note.

methods.name: getTitle
methods.description: Returns the title of the note.

methods.name: getContent
methods.description: Returns the content of the note.

methods.name: getTags
methods.description: Returns the tags associated with the note.

methods.name: getCreatedAt
methods.description: Returns the creation timestamp of the note.

methods.name: getUpdatedAt
methods.description: Returns the last update timestamp of the note.

methods.name: getUpdatedBy
methods.description: Returns the identifier of the last updater.

methods.name: setId
methods.description: Sets the UUID identifier of the note.

methods.name: setTitle
methods.description: Sets the title of the note.

methods.name: setContent
methods.description: Sets the content of the note.

methods.name: setTags
methods.description: Sets the tags associated with the note.

methods.name: setCreatedBy
methods.description: Sets the identifier of the creator.

methods.name: setUpdatedBy
methods.description: Sets the identifier of the last updater.
